该节点涉及的全局状态如下：
  - notification_queue (read_write): Dict mapping notification_id to {type, recipient, content, status, scheduled_at, sent_at}
  - templates (read): Dict mapping template_id to {name, body, channels}
  - delivery_log (read_write): List of {notification_id, channel, status, timestamp, error_msg}

请说明你对每个全局变量的理解。它的数据结构是什么？读写操作分别在什么场景下发生？
